name: 拉斐尔·亨里克斯
name_full: 拉斐尔·亨里克斯 Rafael Henriques
introduction: Rafael Henriques (TV Actor ) was born in Barreiro  on a Friday, August 19, 1994 . Rafael Henriques is 24 years old. He is a Leo  and was born in the Year of the Dog. Big and small screen star who scored his breakout role as Gonçalo in Morangos com Açúcar. He later played prominent roles in Aqui Não Há Quem Viva, Rebelde Way, and Paixão.https://www.birthdaycelebs.com/rafael-henriques/
